I have been struggling with this 30 Day program. In mid-April I started doing a 16 min flexibility for beginners YWA video, a couple times a week as I was recovering from ankle surgery before Christmas. May 1, I started the first of 4 30 day programs. Day 3 or 4 nearly was the end of me LOL, but I stuck it out and saw improvements! Sept came and life and work got crazy. I don't remember thinking before that I just couldn't get into a pose, but now, sometimes, I just can't seem to get anywhere near some. I am going to keep showing up though!! I almost never leave comments under your videos (even though I thank you out loud every single time at the end of practice, Adriene), but today felt different.
